Invocation Name: animal noises
des:
Animal Noises now knows over 195 animal sounds!

THINGS TO TRY
"Alexa, ask Animal Noises to play a t-rex."
"Alexa, tell Animal Noises to surprise me.
"Alexa, ask Animal Noises to list the animals."

UNLOCK MORE SOUNDS
Unlock over 90 new sounds with the Ultimate Expansion Pack, featuring birds from around the world, dinosaurs, mythological creatures, and more.

Tip: Control your sounds! Say "disable dinosaurs" or "disable creatures" and Animal Noises won't play these again unless you ask for them.

FREE SOUNDS
Alligator, Basset Hound, Bat, Bear, Blue Jay, Bobcat, Bumblebee, Butterfly, Camel, Canary, Cardinal, Cat, Cheetah, Chicken, Chimpanzee, Chipmunk, Cicada, Cougar, Cow, Coyote, Crickets, Crocodile, Crow, Deer, Doberman Pincher, Dog, Dolphin, Donkey, Dragon, Duck, Eagle, Elephant, Elk, Finch, Fish, Fly, Fox, Frogs, Gecko, Geese, Giraffe, Gnu, Goat, Gorilla, Guinea Pig, Hippo, Horse, Hyenas, Jaguar, Kitten, Koala Bear, Labrador, Lamb, Lemur, Leopard, Lion, Llama, Lynx, Magpie, Marmot, Mockingbird, Moose, Mosquito, Mountain Lion, Mouse, Owl, Panther, Parakeet, Parrot, Peacock, Pig, Polar Bear, Pony, Prairie Dog, Raccoon, Rat, Rattlesnake, Rhinoceros, Rooster, Sea Lion, Seagulls, Seal, Shark, Sheep, Snake, Spider Monkey, Squirrel, T-rex, Tiger, Turkey, Vulture, Whale, Wolf, Zebra
